welcome_message_body: Welcome to Knik-Fairview, a charming city known for its stunning natural beauty and warm hospitality. We hope you enjoy your stay and take the time to explore all that our city has to offer.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Palmer Municipal Airport serves all commercial and private flights.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Palmer Municipal Airport caters to private and charter flights.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal

terminals.name: South Terminal
